- make sure you are on the proper git branch. If you need other than the last worked on things will surely break ;-)
- make sure you have python3 (/usr/bin/env python3 yields a valid python3 interpreter)
- run ./<repo_dir>/bin/linkConfig.py link <repo_dir>
- copy post-* files to .git/hooks/
- create your own ~/.gitconfig_local file and content (email might not be set)
- open DarkPastel.terminal and then Shell -> Use settings as default (maybe enter terminal settings make a copy of some profile first)


optional:
- change the os level cursor blink
defaults write -g NSTextInsertionPointBlinkPeriod -float 350
defaults write -g NSTextInsertionPointBlinkPeriodOn -float 350
defaults write -g NSTextInsertionPointBlinkPeriodOff -float 350
delete with
#defaults delete -g NSTextInsertionPointBlinkPeriod
